rows.label: tlk47100042_01_msg0001
rows.name:
They say the people of old
must have walked up these
stairs to Fons Maim.

rows.label: tlk47100042_01_msg0002
rows.name:
But ever since fluctuations within the
Divine Beast formed the waters here,
we've had to use Funnystone Highway.

rows.label: tlk47100042_01_msg0003
rows.name:
After that, the residential and
entertainment districts were built over
that way, and naturally, they flourished.

rows.label: tlk47100042_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It's nice that it's so
peaceful and quiet here, but
it gets a little lonely...
